<h1 id="toc0"><span>Come on and slam&#8230;</span></h1>
<p>And welcome to the 144-Hour Jam Contest!</p>
<p>A jam contest, you say? What's that?</p>
<p>It's simple. From March 9th through March 15th, you will write three stories over a six-day period, competing for honor, glory, and meaningless prizes. This contest is designed to squeeze inspiration out of you and see what kind of works you can produce in an accelerated timeframe.</p>
<h1 id="toc1"><span>The Winners</span></h1>
<h3 id="toc2"><span><span style="color: gold"><strong>First place</strong></span> goes to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/not-a-seagull" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3009022); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3009022&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608438389" alt="not_a_seagull" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3009022)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/not-a-seagull" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3009022); return false;">not_a_seagull</a></span>, who secured 275 upvotes across all three of his entries:</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-4808">SCP-4808 - Spontaneous Dog Manifestation</a> (+47) <span style="font-size:smaller;">for Day 1×2</span></li>
<li><a href="/scp-4804">SCP-4804 - The Pulp is Fictional</a> (+70) <span style="font-size:smaller;">for Day 2×2</span></li>
<li><a href="/not-a-seagull-proposal">not_a_seagull's Proposal</a> (+158) <span style="font-size:smaller;">for Day 3×2</span></li>
</ul>
<h3 id="toc3"><span><span style="color: silver"><strong>Second place</strong></span> goes to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/natvoltaic" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2800867); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2800867&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608438389" alt="NatVoltaic" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2800867)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/natvoltaic" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2800867); return false;">NatVoltaic</a></span>, who secured 198 upvotes across all three of her entries:</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-4290">SCP-4290 - The Child Hungers</a> (+156) <span style="font-size:smaller;">for Day 1×2</span></li>
<li><a href="/barrels-of-prose">Barrels of Prose and Slugs of Pulp</a> (+25) <span style="font-size:smaller;">for Day 2×2</span></li>
<li><a href="/sweeter-dreams-inc">Sweeter Dreams Inc.</a> (+17) <span style="font-size:smaller;">for Day 3×2</span></li>
</ul>
<h3 id="toc4"><span><span style="color: goldenrod"><strong>Third place</strong></span> goes to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mortos" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1705184); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1705184&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608438389" alt="Mortos" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1705184)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mortos" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1705184); return false;">Mortos</a></span>, who secured 196 upvotes across his three best entries:</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-4464">SCP-4464 - Dogs Could Be Bigger</a> (+72) <span style="font-size:smaller;">for Day 1×2</span></li>
<li><a href="/scp-4494">SCP-4494 - The Specter Fights For Justice!</a> (+99) <span style="font-size:smaller;">for Day 2×2</span></li>
<li><a href="/scp-4744">SCP-4744 - Stay Woke</a> (+25) <span style="font-size:smaller;">for Day 3×2</span></li>
</ul>
<h2 id="toc5"><span>Additionally, the 2019&#160;144-Hour Jam Contest <span style="color: gold"><strong>GRANDER PRIZE</strong></span> goes to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/natvoltaic" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2800867); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2800867&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608438389" alt="NatVoltaic" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2800867)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/natvoltaic" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2800867); return false;">NatVoltaic</a></span>, who secured 198 upvotes across all three of her uniquely-formatted entries:</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-4290">SCP-4290 - The Child Hungers</a> (+156) <span style="font-size:smaller;">for Day 1×2</span></li>
<li><a href="/barrels-of-prose">Barrels of Prose and Slugs of Pulp</a> (+25) <span style="font-size:smaller;">for Day 2×2</span></li>
<li><a href="/sweeter-dreams-inc">Sweeter Dreams Inc.</a> (+17) <span style="font-size:smaller;">for Day 3×2</span></li>
</ul>
<h3 id="toc6"><span>Congratulations to the winners! Thank you to everyone who participated, and especial thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uraniumempire" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1613974); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1613974&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608438389" alt="UraniumEmpire" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1613974)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uraniumempire" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1613974); return false;">UraniumEmpire</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tsatpwtcotttadc" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3681296); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3681296&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608438389" alt="TSATPWTCOTTTADC" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3681296)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tsatpwtcotttadc" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3681296); return false;">TSATPWTCOTTTADC</a></span> for collecting and tallying up the final scores!</span></h3>
